OL,3,CTikToker 'glamorised suffering for
OL,4,Clikes' in animal fight videos
OL,6,FA man who posted videos on social
OL,7,Fmedia "glamorising the brutal
OL,8,Fsuffering of wild animals" has been
OL,9,Fbanned from keeping dogs for life.
OL,11,FBilly Scarah, 28, filmed dogs fighting
OL,12,Fbadgers and foxes before posting them
OL,13,Fon Facebook and TikTok.
OL,15,FAnimal welfare charity Naturewatch
OL,16,FFoundation reported them to the RSPCA,
OL,17,Fwhich launched an investigation and
OL,18,Ffound a bull lurcher dog called Buddy
OL,19,Fwith severe injuries to its nose
OL,20,Fcaused by a badger.
