OL,3,CTikToker 'glamorised suffering for
OL,4,Clikes' in animal fight videos
OL,6,FRSPCA officer Jason Bowles said: "I
OL,7,Fcould see that he had a large part of
OL,8,Fhis nose missing and the wound looked
OL,9,Fto be healed.
OL,11,F"He also had extensive scarring from
OL,12,Fwounds that looked to be healed on his
OL,13,Fhead and legs. The tip of his tail was
OL,14,Finjured and bleeding."
OL,16,FScarah, of Feldane, Hull, admitted two
OL,17,Foffences of causing unnecessary
OL,18,Fsuffering to a dog and one of
OL,19,Finterfering with a badger sett when he
OL,20,Fappeared at Hull Magistrates' Court.
