OL,6,FHe was given a 12-month suspended
OL,7,Fprison sentence and banned for life
OL,8,Ffrom keeping dogs.
OL,10,FHe was also ordered to pay #600 costs
OL,11,Fand a #187 victim surcharge and to
OL,12,Fcomplete 60 hours of unpaid work.
OL,14,FRSPCA Ch Insp Ian Muttitt said:
OL,15,F"Watching these videos glorifying and
OL,16,Fglamorising the brutal suffering of
OL,17,Fwild animals - and the dogs used to
OL,18,Fhunt them - is shocking. Sadly, this
OL,19,Fis something that can easily be found
OL,20,Fon many of the social media platforms
OL,21,Ftoday.
