OL,6,FSgt Kevin Jones, of Humberside Police,
OL,7,Fsaid: "The persecution of badgers is a
OL,8,FUK wildlife crime priority and a
OL,9,Fpriority for the Humberside Police
OL,10,FRural Task Force. Not only does it
OL,11,Finvolve barbaric acts of cruelty
OL,12,Fagainst badgers, but it also causes
OL,13,Fhorrific injuries to the dogs
OL,14,Finvolved."
OL,16,FBuddy was taken into RSPCA care before
OL,17,Fbeing rehomed.
